段正澄院士，因病在武汉去世。
Academician Duan Zhengcheng died in Wuhan due to illness.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 邓雅菲据@光明日报 消息，中国工程院院士、华中科技大学机械科学与工程学院教授、制造装备数字化国家工程研究中心首席科学家、机械制造与自动化专家段正澄，因病于2020年2月15日在武汉去世。
Pang Pai journalist Deng Yafei, academician of the Chinese Academy of Engineering, professor at the School of Mechanical Sciences and Engineering of Huazhong University of Science and Technology, chief scientist at the National Engineering Research Center for Digitalization of Manufacturing Equipment and expert Zhengcheng Duan, a mechanic and automation expert, died in Wuhan on February 15, 2020.
公开资料显示，段正澄院士是机械制造与自动化（加工技术和装备）专家。
Open data shows that the Zheng Cheng academician is an expert in mechanical manufacturing and automation (processing technology and equipment).
汉族，中共党员，江苏省镇江市人，机械制造与自动化专家。
Han nationality, member of CPC, native of Zhenjiang, Jiangsu Province, expert in mechanical manufacturing and automation.
1957年毕业于华中工学院（现华中科技大学）机械系，后留校工作至今，长期从事机械制造与自动化学科的教学与科研工作。
Graduated in 1957 from the Central China Institute of Technology (now Huazhong University of Science and Technology) Department of Machinery, after the work of the University has long been engaged in machinery manufacturing and automation teaching and research work.
他一直工作在一线，与生产紧密结合，致力于国家重要需求的自动化、数字化加工技术与装备的应用基础研究和工程技术研发。
He has been working on the front line, closely integrated with production, and is committed to the automation of important national needs, digital processing technology and equipment applied basic research and engineering technology development.
现为华中科技大学机械学院教授、博士研究生导师、制造装备数字化国家工程研究中心首席科学家。
He is currently Professor, Doctorate Postgraduate Tutor and Chief Scientist, National Engineering Research Center for Digital Manufacturing Equipment, Central China University of Science and Technology.
段正澄先后获得1978年全国科学大会奖2项、国家科学技术进步一等奖1项、二等奖3项；省部级科学技术进步特等奖1项、一等奖7项、二等奖4项；2011年获湖北省科学技术突出贡献奖；发表论文200余篇。
Duan Zhengcheng won two National Science and Technology Congress awards in 1978, one first-class prize and three second-class prizes. He won one special prize, seven first-class prizes and four second-class prizes for scientific and technological progress at the provincial and ministerial levels.
先后被评为全国优秀教师、湖北省劳动模范、湖北省先进教育工作者和湖北省先进科技工作者。
He was successively awarded as an outstanding teacher in China, a model worker in Hubei Province, an advanced educator in Hubei Province and an advanced scientific worker in Hubei Province.
他所领导的教学与科研团队，1993年被评为全国先进集体，并获得“五一”劳动奖状。
His teaching and scientific research team, in 1993, was awarded the national advanced collective, and won the "May 1" labor award.
2009年当选为中国工程院院士。
Elected member of the Chinese Academy of Engineering in 2009.
中国工程院院士、华中科技大学机械科学与工程学院教授段正澄。
Zhang Zhengcheng, Academician of Chinese Academy of Engineering and Professor of Mechanical Science and Engineering of Huazhong University of Technology.
华中科技大学 资料图搞科研要经得起“脉冲”段正澄院士将毕生的精力奉献给了国家科技事业。
The data plan of Huazhong University of Science and Technology should stand up to the impulse of academician devoting his whole life to the cause of national science and technology.
六十多年来，他坚持深入一线企业合作，以机械制造及自动化学科为基础，面向国家重大需求，开展多学科交叉与集成，进行高端装备的创新研究和工程化开发，研发了多台（套）国际、国内首创的高端自动化装备、并在湖北实现了产业化。
For more than 60 years, he has persisted in deepening cooperation with leading-edge enterprises, basing himself on mechanical manufacturing and automation, facing the country's major needs, carrying out multidisciplinary cross-cutting and integration, carrying out innovative research and engineering development of high-end equipment, and developing high-end automation equipment (sets) pioneered internationally and domestically, and realizing industrialization in Hubei.
2009年，75岁高龄的段正澄获选为中国工程院院士。
In 2009, the 75-year-old Duan Zhengcheng was elected a member of the Chinese Academy of Engineering.
据《楚天都市报》此前报道，曾经有人鼓励段正澄参选院士，他却拒绝了。
The Chu Tian Metropolis Daily had previously reported that Mr. Duan had been encouraged to run for academician, but he refused.
老人把“院士”的头衔看得极淡，在他看来，扎扎实实搞科研才是自己兴趣所在。
The old man regarded the title of academician very lightly. In his opinion, it was his interest to engage in scientific research.
“从事科学研究也许十年二十年都不会有什么大的成果，因此绝不能浮躁，不能急功近利。
"Scientific research may not yield great results in a decade or two, so it must not be impetuous or expedient.
选准了目标，就要长期坚持，百折不挠。
If you choose your goal, you must persevere and persevere.
只有这样，才能出成果，出大成果。
Only in this way can results be achieved and results achieved.
”对于坚持的意义，段正澄有着特别深刻体会，他形象地说：“做研究要耐得住寂寞，不能外面来一个脉冲，自己就要震荡。
"Duan Zhengcheng had a deep understanding of the meaning of persistence, and said vividly:" Do research to endure loneliness, can not come outside a pulse, their own oscillation.
”段正澄院士为湖北的经济发展、科技进步以及人才培养做出了突出贡献。
Academician Duan Zhengcheng made outstanding contributions to Hubei's economic development, scientific and technological progress and personnel training.
在2011年度湖北省科技奖励大会上，获湖北省科学技术突出贡献奖的段正澄院士平静地说，“我将以诚惶诚恐之心对待这次的荣誉，以兢兢业业之心对待今后的工作。
At the 2011 Hubei Provincial Science and Technology Awards Conference, the distinguished scholar Duan Zhengcheng, who won the prize for outstanding contributions to science and technology in Hubei Province, calmly said, "I will treat this honor with sincere fear and treat the future work with dedication.
”“这里有我栽下的树，还有影响我一生的师长”1953年，19岁的段正澄成为华中工学院（现华中科技大学）成立后招收的第一届大学生，1957年毕业留校任教，从此扎根喻园，一呆就是60多年。
"In 1953, Duan Zhengcheng, 19, became the first college student admitted after the founding of the Central China Institute of Technology (now Huazhong University of Science and Technology).
他曾说，“这里有我栽下的树，还有影响我一生的师长”。
He once said, "Here are the trees I planted, and the teachers who have influenced me all my life."
据《武汉晚报》此前报道，20世纪50年代的华中工学院初建阶段，段正澄和同学都要在节假日参加基建工作，常常是上午种树，下午在工地当小工，“现在的东二楼东三楼都有我挑过的砖。
According to an earlier report by Wuhan Evening News, in the early 1950s, Duan Zhengcheng and his classmates were going to take part in the construction work on holidays, often planting trees in the morning and working at the construction site in the afternoon.
把一个大食堂用砖头分成许多格，每格就是一间教室。
Divide a large cafeteria into blocks, each of which is a classroom.
”回忆起这段建校岁月，段正澄感慨地说：“虽然生活艰苦，但很磨练人的意志。
"Recalling this period of school, paragraph Cheng Cheng said with emotion:" Although life is difficult, but very hone the will.
而且正是因为亲自参与了，所以有着特别的荣誉感，愿意为学校的发展壮大作出自己的努力。
And it is because of personal participation, so there is a special sense of honor, willing to make their own efforts for the development of the school.
”母校团结、和谐的环境和氛围一直是段正澄最留恋的地方，“1953年的华中工学院是由数所学校的一些专业合并而成的。
The harmonious environment and atmosphere of his alma mater had always been the most attractive place for Cheng. "In 1953, the Central China Institute of Technology was a merger of some specialties from several schools.
从建立起，学校领导就非常注重营造一种团结、协作的氛围。
From its inception, school leaders have placed great emphasis on creating an atmosphere of solidarity and collaboration.
虽然教师们来自不同学校不同专业，但相互之间的那种关心互助，深深影响了我们那群学生。
Although the teachers come from different schools and specialties, the mutual care and mutual help deeply affect our group of students.
人心齐，泰山移，这是一片造就人才、成就事业的沃土。
This is a fertile land for the creation of talented people and the achievement of career.
”据华中科技大学官网资料介绍，段正澄在华中科技大学任教期间，先后获1978年全国科学大会奖2项、国家科技进步二等奖3项；省部级一等奖5项、二等奖4项；发表论文217篇，三大索引收录78篇；主编《光机电一体化手册》，参编《机械工程手册》，编写教材4本；获授权专利19项(发明专利5项)。
During his tenure at Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Mr. Duan won two National Science Congress awards in 1978 and three state science and technology second-class awards.
大师远去，荣光犹存。
The Master is gone, the glory is still there.
本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
